en: Nathalie, Didier and their children, Sacha and Dimitri, will be happy to welcome you for a moment of relaxation and well being in the heart of their 8-hectare estate with swimming pool and spa, Cabanes et Bulles stands in the heart of the Cévennes forest for unusual nights under the stars. Comfort and charm in addition, all is located on the mountainside in a preserved nature. Each bubble, dome or pyramid without any opposite has its own private jaccuzzi. Open from April to September 31st. What do you want to do ? New mail Copy
